responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "2EF1926B402FA66D7C527989E4D8C49E", "Our negotiations with the neighboring vassals grow strained as our resources dwindle. To make matters worse, the rainfall has flooded our grain stores, setback our attacking force, and has caused severe strain on our livelihoods. We must avail ourselves of every means available to us. If you find your way to the Honorsworn Keep, you might find whether the mystics have recovered anything else of value.")
